聆听 The Smile 令人难忘的新单曲“Bodies Laughing” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-smile-haunting-new-single-bodies-laughing-3799266?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-the-smile-haunting-新的单身机构笑Liberty DunworthThu, 03 Oct 2024 09:52:34 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3799266 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="微笑，2024" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>它标志着即将发行的专辑“Cutouts”中的最新歌曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-smile-haunting-new-single-bodies-laughing-3799266">Listen to The Smile 令人难忘的新单曲“Bodies Laughing”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="微笑，2024" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The-Smile@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smile">The Smile</a>分享了一首忧郁的新单曲，名为“Bodies Laughing”——请在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-smile-cutouts-review-3799173">The Smile – “Cutouts”评论：Radiohead 的副项目陷入困境</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>该曲目于今天（10 月 3 日）发行，是乐队新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-smile-cutouts-review-3799173">Cutouts</a> 》中分享的最新单曲，该专辑将于明天通过 XL Recordings 发行 - <a href="https://shop.xlrecordings.com/release/469975-the-smile-cutouts?lang=en_GB" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处预订。</a></p><p>这首歌是唱片中节奏较柔和的曲目之一，并以令人难忘的器乐旋律缓缓进入开场主歌。 “<em>左右摇摆/下巴张开/藏在我的帽子下</em>，”<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thom-yorke">汤姆·约克（Thom Yorke）</a>在歌曲逐渐形成动力时唱道。 “<em>只是为了让你生气/只是为了惹恼你/漂浮在他们的背上</em>。”</p><p>看看下面的内容，以及充满活力、僵尸风格的可视化工具。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="微笑 - 笑的身体（可视化工具）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EWpI0n1FZIY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Bodies Laughing》是《Cutouts》在明天发行之前分享的第五首单曲。早期的单曲包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-smile-announce-new-album-cutouts-with-two-singles-foreign-spies-and-zero-sum-3788255">《外国间谍》、《零和》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-smiles-trippy-new-single-dont-get-me-started-3782074">《别让我开始》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-smiles-surprise-new-songs-dont-get-me-started-and-the-slip-3780679">《The Slip》。</a></p><p>后两张最近在世界各地的唱片店以限量版双轨 12 英寸单曲的形式发行，在明天发行完整唱片后，The Smile 还将发布一段由 Weirdcore 执导的全新视频。曲目“即时诗篇”。</p><p>虽然《Bodies Laughing》今天早上（10 月 3 日）才正式发布，但由 Yorke、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jonny-greenwood">Jonny Greenwood</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sons-of-kemet">Sons Of Kemet</a>鼓手 Tom Skinner 组成的三人组自 2022 年以来一直在戏弄这首单曲。</p><p>当乐队当年开始欧洲巡回演唱会时，它首次出现在歌迷面前，以支持他们的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-smile-a-light-for-attracting-attention-radiohead-thom-yorke-jonny-greenwood-3222308">《A Light For Attracting Attracting Attention》</a> 。</p><p>他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-side-project-the-smile-debut-new-song-bodies-laughing-footage-watch-3234348">在柏林 Tempodrom 场地的演出中演奏了这首歌</a>，主唱告诉观众：“所以，昨天我们写了另一首新歌……我们要尝试演奏它。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="微笑 - 笑的身体（彩虹中缺少歌曲？）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HEkUaenhWiw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>自 2022 年首次亮相以来，乐队于今年年初发行了他们的第二张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-smile-wall-of-eyes-review-lyrics-3573993">《Wall Of Eyes》</a> 。</p><p>在明天正式发行之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-smile-cutouts-review-3799173" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>NME</em>给予《Cutouts》四星评价</a>，并形容乐队“似乎比以往任何时候都更有趣”。</p><p> “那么，《微笑》的 MO 似乎是一种实验，没有约克和格林伍德膨胀的背部目录的包袱——而《剪纸》无疑在这里实现了，”它写道。 “这张专辑以伦敦当代交响乐团为特色，与《Wall of Eyes》一起在牛津和艾比路录音室录制，但这张专辑比前一张专辑更自由、更有趣。</p><p> “这张唱片夸耀的是《Bending Hectic》，一首郁郁葱葱的八分钟民谣，最后陷入锯齿状的不和谐音，让<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lou-reed">Lou Reed</a>听起来像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aqua">Aqua</a> ，而这张唱片则呈现了《Instant Psalm》，一首昏昏欲睡的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pop">流行歌曲</a>，传达了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>的印度古典阶段”。</p><p>本周早些时候，乐队开始通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-smile-announce-electronic-art-installations-new-album-cutouts-london-nyc-3798737">在纽约和伦敦举行的一系列“Through The Glass”活动</a>预览这张专辑。这些活动包括来自 Weirdcore 的独家视觉效果以及在明天发行前解锁专辑曲目的代码。</p><p>微笑乐队今年一直忙于巡演，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-smile-cancel-tour-as-jonny-greenwood-recovers-from-intensive-care-stay-3774522">由于格林伍德生病并在重症监护后需要时间康复，不得不取消八月份的多个欧洲巡演日期</a>。与此同时，Yorke 将于本月晚些时候到 11 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thom-yorke-announces-solo-tour-with-dates-in-australia-singapore-and-more-3761682">前往澳大利亚、新西兰、新加坡和日本进行巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-smile-haunting-new-single-bodies-laughing-3799266">Listen to The Smile 令人难忘的新单曲“Bodies Laughing”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
